. Set Varoma into position, insert Varoma tray and place in chicken packets, secure Varoma lid and steam <b>22 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>."},{"content":"Carefully open Varoma lid, add broccoli florets and steam a further <b>8 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>."},{"content":"Remove chicken from parchment and brush with balsamic glaze, to taste. Garnish with chopped fresh basil and serve hot with steamed broccoli."}],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","55m","2 portions"]}